{"type":"message","id":"1ef9b004","parentId":"67a854ed","timestamp":"2026-02-20T06:07:00.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! MEMORY.md shows they have a Google Sheets setup for inventory and cleaning. That's useful context.\n\nNow, the runtime info shows:\n- model: openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n- default_model: openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n\nThey're the same, so I don't need to mention the default model.\n\nBased on SOUL.md's guidance:\n- Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful (skip \"great to meet you!\")\n- Concise when needed\n- Not a corporate drone or sycophant\n- Just good\n\nSince this is a new session and I don't have a defined persona yet (IDENTITY.md is empty), I should just be straightforward and direct per SOUL.md's guidance. I'll keep it brief and ask what they want to do.\n\n1-3 sentences, ask what they want to do.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I'm here and ready to help. What's on your mind?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":145,"output":390,"cacheRead":14400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14935,"cost":{"input":0.000055100000000000004,"output":0.000663,"cacheRead":0.002736,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034541}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771567611730}}
